      "comment": "Known iCloud Error.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Permission Failure: to use this app, you must enable iCloud Drive. Go to device Settings, sign in to iCloud, then in the app settings, be sure the iCloud Drive feature is enabled."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Berechtigungsfehler: Um diese App verwenden zu können, müssen Sie iCloud Drive aktivieren. Gehen Sie zu den Geräteeinstellungen, melden Sie sich bei iCloud an und stellen Sie dann in den App-Einstellungen sicher, dass die iCloud Drive-Funktion aktiviert ist."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Échec d'autorisation : pour utiliser cette application, vous devez activer iCloud Drive. Accédez aux paramètres de l'appareil, connectez-vous à iCloud, puis dans les paramètres de l'application, assurez-vous que la fonctionnalité iCloud Drive est activée."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Error de permiso: para utilizar esta aplicación, debe habilitar iCloud Drive. Vaya a Configuración del dispositivo, inicie sesión en iCloud y luego, en la configuración de la aplicación, asegúrese de que la función iCloud Drive esté habilitada."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Errore di autorizzazione: per utilizzare questa app, devi abilitare iCloud Drive. Vai alle Impostazioni del dispositivo, accedi a iCloud, quindi nelle impostazioni dell'app, assicurati che la funzione iCloud Drive sia abilitata."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "权限失败：要使用此应用程序，您必须启用 iCloud Drive。前往设备设置，登录 iCloud，然后在应用程序设置中确保 iCloud Drive 功能已启用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "label.text.please-add-the-feedly-account-again-if-this-problem-persists-open-keychain-access-and-delete-all-feedly-com-entries-then-try-again": {
      "comment": "Feedly – Credentials not found.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Please add the Feedly account again. If this problem persists, open Keychain Access and delete all feedly.com entries, then try again."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bitte fügen Sie das Feedly-Konto erneut hinzu. Wenn das Problem weiterhin besteht, öffnen Sie die Schlüsselbundverwaltung, löschen Sie alle Einträge auf „feedly.com“ und versuchen Sie es dann erneut."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Veuillez ajouter à nouveau le compte Feedly. Si ce problème persiste, ouvrez Trousseau Access et supprimez toutes les entrées feedly.com, puis réessayez."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Por favor agregue la cuenta Feedly nuevamente. Si este problema persiste, abra Acceso a Llaveros y elimine todas las entradas de feedly.com, luego intente nuevamente."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aggiungi nuovamente l'account Feedly. Se il problema persiste, apri Accesso Portachiavi ed elimina tutte le voci di feedly.com, quindi riprova."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请重新添加 Feedly 帐户。如果此问题仍然存在，请打开钥匙串访问并删除所有 feedly.com 条目，然后重试。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
