    "label.text.sign-in-to-your-bazqux-account-and-sync-your-feeds-across-your-devices-your-username-and-password-will-be-encrypted-and-stored-in-keychain-dont-have-a-bazqux-account": {
      "comment": "Text shown in the app interface: \"Sign in to your BazQux account and sync your feeds across your devices. Your username and password will be encrypted and stored in Keychain. Don’t have a BazQux account?\".",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sign in to your BazQux account and sync your feeds across your devices. Your username and password will be encrypted and stored in Keychain.\n\nDon’t have a BazQux account?"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Melden Sie sich bei Ihrem BazQux-Konto an und synchronisieren Sie Ihre Feeds auf Ihren Geräten. Ihr Benutzername und Ihr Passwort werden verschlüsselt und im Schlüsselbund gespeichert.\n\nSie haben kein BazQux-Konto?"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Connectez-vous à votre compte BazQux et synchronisez vos flux sur vos appareils. Votre nom d'utilisateur et votre mot de passe seront cryptés et stockés dans le trousseau.\n\nVous n'avez pas de compte BazQux ?"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Inicie sesión en su cuenta BazQux y sincronice sus feeds en sus dispositivos. Su nombre de usuario y contraseña se cifrarán y almacenarán en Keychain.\n\n¿No tienes una cuenta de BazQux?"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Accedi al tuo account BazQux e sincronizza i tuoi feed sui tuoi dispositivi. Il tuo nome utente e la tua password verranno crittografati e archiviati nel portachiavi.\n\nNon hai un account BazQux?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "登录您的 BazQux 帐户并在您的设备上同步您的源。您的用户名和密码将被加密并存储在钥匙串中。\n\n没有 BazQux 帐户？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
