    "label.text.sign-in-to-your-feedbin-account-and-sync-your-feeds-across-your-devices-your-username-and-password-will-be-encrypted-and-stored-in-keychain-dont-have-a-feedbin-account": {
      "comment": "Text shown in the app interface: \"Sign in to your Feedbin account and sync your feeds across your devices. Your username and password will be encrypted and stored in Keychain. Don’t have a Feedbin account?\".",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sign in to your Feedbin account and sync your feeds across your devices. Your username and password will be encrypted and stored in Keychain.\n\nDon’t have a Feedbin account?"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Melden Sie sich bei Ihrem Feedbin-Konto an und synchronisieren Sie Ihre Feeds auf Ihren Geräten. Ihr Benutzername und Ihr Passwort werden verschlüsselt und im Schlüsselbund gespeichert.\n\nSie haben kein Feedbin-Konto?"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Connectez-vous à votre compte Feedbin et synchronisez vos flux sur vos appareils. Votre nom d'utilisateur et votre mot de passe seront cryptés et stockés dans le trousseau.\n\nVous n'avez pas de compte Feedbin ?"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Inicie sesión en su cuenta de Feedbin y sincronice sus feeds en sus dispositivos. Su nombre de usuario y contraseña se cifrarán y almacenarán en Keychain.\n\n¿No tienes una cuenta de Feedbin?"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Accedi al tuo account Feedbin e sincronizza i tuoi feed sui tuoi dispositivi. Il tuo nome utente e la tua password verranno crittografati e archiviati nel portachiavi.\n\nNon hai un account Feedbin?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "登录您的 Feedbin 帐户并在您的设备上同步您的 Feed。您的用户名和密码将被加密并存储在钥匙串中。\n\n没有 Feedbin 帐户？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
